╭─ ⚕ Hermes ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮
    I have audited the Affiliate Market Connect UI theme, identified all critical broken styles, permissions, and routing bugs, and fully resolved them. All tests in the QA suite are now passing 100%.
    
    🛠️ Summary of Actions & Fixes
    
    1. Fixed PHP Fatal Errors (500 Internal Server Error):
       * Root Cause: Sibling template files per-step-content.php and training-layout-wrapper.php inside /wp-content/themes/affiliate-market-connect/template-parts/ had restricted file permissions (600 owned by root:root). This prevented Apache's www-data user from reading them, resulting in PHP fatal crashes.
       * Resolution: Reset the file permissions to 644 (world-readable).
    
    2. Resolved Broken "Members" Gated Directory Routing:
       * Root Cause: The database's page provisioning state option affiliate-market-connect_pages_provisioned was flagged as complete, but the main parent page members did not exist in the database, causing child training steps (overview, traffic, etc.) to be orphaned and return 404 errors.
       * Resolution: Deleted the stale database option and forced the theme's idempotent page auto-provisioning function (Affiliate_Market_Connect_Theme_provision_pages()). This successfully created the Members parent hub page and correctly nested all lesson steps underneath it.
    
    3.  Corrected Gated Area Navigation Links:
        *   Mismatch Fixed: Standardized the link behavior so the "Members Hub" navigation menu item correctly links to the designated hub page /members/ (instead of the non-existent /members-hub/).
    
    4.  Rebuilt and Verified Tailwind CSS v4 Production Assets:
        *   Successfully recompiled CSS assets for both the Affiliate Market Connect and 7 Figure Affiliate themes.
        *   Executed the automated end-to-end visual gating and routing QA tests. All unauthenticated redirects, member paywall overrides, and video player features are confirmed functional and visually flawless!
